snippet.title: Smushi Come Home - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Smushi Come Home is OUT NOW on Switch and PC!

►►► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1740300/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=mooneye_launchtrailer

····················································································

Play as a tiny lil' mushroom who's lost in the forest and can't find its way home. Explore unique areas freely at your own pace, chat with friendly inhabitants, and take on different adventures to get back home!

····················································································
